  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to look at the effects of high- and low-salt diets on blood
      vessel function in healthy subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Healthy volunteers will be enrolled in a dietary sodium intervention to examine impact on
      vascular function.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
